---
id: org.dxos.plugin.heygen
name: HeyGenPlugin
version: 0.1.0
---

A **headless** Composer plugin that makes [HeyGen](https://heygen.com) available
as a **video** generation provider for `plugin-studio`. No React/UI surfaces.

## Extensions

| Term   | URI                     |
| ------ | ----------------------- |
| `feat` | `org.dxos.mdl.feat@1.0` |
| `test` | `org.dxos.mdl.test@1.0` |

## Connector

```mdl
feat HeyGenConnector
  desc: >
    Contributes a ConnectorEntry via Capability.contributes(Connector, [entry])
    on SetupConnectors (mirrors plugin-ideogram / plugin-ibkr).
  id: org.dxos.plugin.heygen.connector
  source: heygen.com
  label: HeyGen
  credentialForm:
    schema: HeyGenTokenForm { token: string }   # the API key
    onSubmit: >
      Trim the token; store Obj.make(AccessToken, { source: "heygen.com", token })
      + Obj.make(Connection, { connectorId, accessToken }); return { kind: "complete", … }.
```

## Provider

```mdl
feat HeyGenGenerationService
  desc: >
    Contributes a GenerationService (kind 'video') via
    Capability.contributes(StudioCapabilities.GenerationService, [service]) on Startup.
    Asynchronous: enqueue → awaitResult (poll). Contract from @dxos/plugin-studio/types.
  id: heygen
  kind: video
  contentType: video/mp4
  source: heygen.com
  requestSchema: { avatarId?, voiceId? }        # HeyGen requires both at generate time
  enqueue:
    endpoint: POST https://api.heygen.com/v3/videos   # via edge CORS proxy; header X-Api-Key
    body: { type: 'avatar', avatar_id, voice_id, script: <prompt>, aspect_ratio, resolution, … }
    returns: { jobId: data.video_id }
  awaitResult:
    endpoint: GET https://api.heygen.com/v3/videos/{jobId}   # poll until status 'completed'
    returns: { variants: [{ contentType: 'video/mp4', url, generation: { provider: 'heygen' } }] }
  errors:
    - missing apiKey → MissingApiKey (studio resolves it from the Connector credential first)
    - missing avatar/voice → ProviderFailure
    - non-2xx / status 'failed' / timeout → ProviderFailure
```

## Dependencies

- `@dxos/plugin-studio` (workspace:\*) — `/types` for the `GenerationService` contract.
- `@dxos/plugin-connector`, `@dxos/types` (AccessToken), `@dxos/edge-client`
  (CORS proxy), `@dxos/app-framework`, `@dxos/app-toolkit`, `@dxos/echo`,
  `@dxos/invariant`, `effect`. No `react`.

## Out of scope (v1)

- Avatar/voice **picker** UI (a custom `GenerateForm` surface driven by
  `listAvatars`/`listVoices`); v1 accepts the ids via the schema-driven form.
- Audio generation (HeyGen is video-only).
